node.text: We’re joining forces with our friends in the #Austin restaurant industry for #ComeAndTakeOutATX today. node.text: It’s the people that make this place so special. From all us to all of you...we’d like to say THANK YOU for this community rallying around our little bbq business. We had a busy Easter weekend selling out yesterday very early in the day and overwhelmed by the support. Trying to keep up with this new way of operating is not easy in craft style bbq, but we are so thankful to be operating. We cannot thank you enough for the much needed support for this amazing staff...which is our secret sauce. We hope we are able to provide a little bit of normalcy for you and your family though the meals we cook. Your kindness is being payed forward more than you know. With that, we are Closed on Mondays every week and this week we have decided to let our pits rest and have our very hard working crew take an extra day off this coming Tuesday so that we can all spend some time to recharge and reset with our families. So, from all of us to all of you...Thank Ya Kindly Austin, Texas. We will see you this Wednesday at Stiles Switch BBQ rested, recharged and ready to cook some BBQ in the greatest city on the planet. #TexasBBQ #StilesSwitchBBQ #ToSmallToFail #AustinTexas #ATX #BBQ #Austin #AustinBBQ #ATX #Barbecue #TMBBQTop50 #AustinStrong #StillHereATX #Austin360Eats #AustinFoodie please note: we don’t own the rights to this music but on any given day that you walk in our Pitroom you will hear @sturgillsimpson keeping our spirits high and rolling through the nights smoking some meats. #MusicHeals support your artists where you. We sure do need them now more than ever. @myhaam is a great local place to lend a hand if you can.

node.text: We’ve got a Sunday special coming at ya! Pitmaster Braun Hughes @braun_hughes is back with his Rattlesnake BBQ Sauced Oak Smoked Wings! Whatever ya do this Sunday, don’t skip these wings. Oak Smoked, flash fried sauced and tossed to order. #ChickenWings #TexasBBQ #AustinTexas #ATX #Barbecue #CedarParkTX

node.text: The morning hustle. Sunday is looking nice. Slow living and Smoked Meats are on this menu today. Don’t be in a hurry and we will see ya starting at 11am. #AustinTexas #BBQ #Barbecue #ATX #SmokedMeats #Sunday

🔈 “East Bound & Down…” Raise up a Diablo Sandwich today & Welcome Buford T. to the #StilesSwitchBBQ Pitroom on North Lamar. You think you’ve had a busy morning…we are adding a new pit and doing some rearranging and making room for more pits and it’s all hands on deck today. Sunny Moberg @sunnyinaustin @mobergsmokers you’ve out done yourself on this paint job. Buford T. is a 1000 Gallon Brisket smoking beast. Black Paint with Gold paint Flecks that shine real nice in that hot Texas sun. Now come get a Diablo Sandwich & a Dr. Peppa..and don’t be in a GD Hurry. This is #Texas #Craft #BBQ at #StilesSwitchBBQ in #AustinTexas more pics of Buford in the stories and the pit rearrange job today that is no joke. #AustinTexas #CedarParkTX #BBQ #OldAustin #VioletCrown #PitBuilder #Moberg
